text:
Honestly it's just another Shell petrol kiosk. Nothing too special about them vs the others that you'd find around the area.

If any, it's a very hard-to-find petrol kiosk, and it's not difficult to miss seeing them if you're coming from Tiong Bahru side of things, because of the overhead bridge blocking the logo whilst driving. You'd need to be intentional to find them here; passed by this road so many times over, but never knew they were here.
As a fuel station, they also have a recycle box for electronic waste. At that time, I put my water boiler here.

Forget all other fuel stations. This is your new regular!

Pumping staff are friendly and will put a smile on your face and the counter staff were quick and polite.
Very nice and friendly pump attendant. Counter staff is a little inexperienced.
Nice little neighbourhood petrol kiosk with friendly and kind pump attendants.
